{
  "texts": [
    "The participants' voices were recorded during the administration of these two tests, and the collected data was utilized for further analyses.",
    "The average duration of the protocol was 109.07 ± 15.54 s, with a minimum and maximum duration of 74.6 and 158.9 s respectively.",
    "The audio recordings were standardized to a frequency of 16 KHz, removing initial and final silent portions and applying the noise reduction model presented in [45] to eliminate potential environmental artifacts.",
    "The resulting audio data were manually reviewed.",
    "Then, features were extracted from the standardized feature set eGeMAPS [15] using the Python interface of the opensource toolkit OpenSMile [46]."
  ]
}